gw.cc.bizrules

Interface ActivityRulesVersionController

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BizRulesVersionController<ActivityRule,ActivityRuleVersion,ActivityRuleHead>

    public interface ActivityRulesVersionController
extends BizRulesVersionController<ActivityRule,ActivityRuleVersion,ActivityRuleHead>
    ActivityRulesVersionController governs the mechanism for storing ActivityRule, ActivityRuleVersion and ActivityRuleHead for business rules. Each new business rule entity will need its own controller interface and implementation.
